| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0984 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 581a0ad9-fcc0-520a-8a97-9a7672a04e8c"
